Following changes have been made to the source licensed under Apache 2.0

* Remove vulnerability identification numbers
* Change standard NTP server
* Remove ./tasks/pkgupdate.yml
* SSHd config
    - Allow remote root login
    - Comment out "IgnoreUserKnownHosts yes"
    - Remove banner
    - Increase ClientAliveCountMax
* Modify Lynis command and added post-processing
* Remove auditd

The specific changes can be found in the repo https://github.com/Liblor/applied_sec_lab, with
`git log --name-status ./applied_sec_lab/vagrant_share/ansible/roles/hardening`
